What's possible for Iowa football the rest of this season? 
An undefeated regular-season romp and a Big Ten championship-game berth are certainly within reach. 
Rick Brown, Chad Leistikow and Ross Peterson recap the possibilities in a bonus segment not heard on the radio and sprinkle in some wrestling news, to boot. Read or Share this story: http://dmreg.co/1RXr24J MORE STORIES
